cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.SOC, cs.DL, cs.LG 

This paper deals with social tagging data and recommendation algorithms, which are commonly studied in the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses graph models and extensions of FolkRank, which are relevant to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Deep Learning (cs.DL) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper analyzes the characteristics of social tagging data, which falls under the Social and Information Networks (cs.SOC) sub-category.
